name: "what will i become?"
description:
rinrinarts, [31.10.21 16:54]
*THIS IS A NON-CANON GODH GIRL SPIN OFF*

GODH GIRL journey started from inside a lab, cultured inside a fluid pod.

Is she human? A lab-grown human? Or nothing more than just a soul-less shell?

Unknowingly, she is already living among us. If you have never realized this, then I suggest you to start looking.

Or...
perhaps...
maybe...
you...
are...

one of them?
